# Testing & Validation Strategy

## Test Plan
- Unit tests for each gameplay loop module and controller.
- Integration tests for narrative branches and world state changes.
- Automated validation for mod/plugin APIs and onboarding scripts.

## Artifact-Driven Test Cases
- Test cases are defined and tracked as artifacts for traceability.
- Validation scripts ensure all systems align with the intended gameplay experience.

